1)Write a java Program to create an integer array by taking length as 
input from the user .  take the contents of the array from user and store 
the contents in the array. Display the contents of the array on to the console.



2) Write a java Program to create an integer array by taking length as 
input from the user .  take the contents of the array from user and store 
the contents in the array. Display the contents of the array by incrementing 
each value present in the array by 5  on to the console.

Note  : Use Enhanced For Loop


3) Write a java program to take array length as input from user and create an 
integer array . Create an integer array and store elements into the array 
by taking elements as input from keyboard. 
Print the array contents on to console if array content is positive.